<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body class="container py-4">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
      <h3 class="mb-0">Datos bancarios para depósitos</h3>
      <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="/admin">Volver al panel</a>
    </div>

    <form action="/admin/banco" method="post" class="row g-3">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <label class="form-label">Banco</label>
        <input class="form-control" name="bank_name" value="<%= b.bank_name || '' %>" required>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">
        <label class="form-label">Cuenta / CLABE / tarjeta</label>
        <input class="form-control" name="bank_account" value="<%= b.bank_account || '' %>" required>
      </div>

      <div class="col-12">
        <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
          La referencia se genera automáticamente con el <strong>teléfono</strong> del titular
          y el monto con el <strong>total de la reserva</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-12">
        <button class="btn btn-primary">Guardar</button>
      </div>
    </form>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>